title.rendered: Channing Tatum and Jenna Dewan: Engaged!

content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

We’re really sorry, ladies.

But hunky actor Channing Tatum is engaged to girlfriend Jenna Dewan.

Over the weekend, Tatum reportedly asked her for Dewan’s hand in marriage in Maui in front of close friends invited under the radar to surprise Dewan. The pair met on the set of 2006’s Step Up, while Tatum will star in the anticipated G.I. Joe movie in 2009.

Channing Tatum proposed to Jenna Dewan over the weekend. Obviously, she said yes.
